Dear friends, happy Saturday!
The weather wasn't very cooperative last week, so we flew again today.
Powered stall recovery, unpowered stall recovery, slow flight, simulated engine failure (!), route training, three landings and one go-around with the help of the instructor.
Everything is good ^_^
